# Runtime cache files — generated at startup, not source code
# NOTE: .sql_template_cache.json is intentionally NOT ignored. It is a build
# artifact: pre-compiled MetricFlow SQL templates (see precompile_templates.py)
# committed to the repo so production never runs the 30-45s MetricFlow
# subprocess. Regenerate and re-commit it after any dbt semantic model change.
.query_cache.json
